{"route":{"route":"/posts/afc6d6dd/","outputPath":"posts/afc6d6dd/index.html","kind":"post","title":"Hyperledger Fabric组织更换证书","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"afc6d6dd"}},"description":"前言 最近一直在研究关于如何给一个fabric的组织更换一个新的证书, 包括所有加入的通道, 所有peer和orderer. 用了很多看似完美的方法却多次测试失败, 最后总算找到一种方法. 一个通道配置块类似上面这种,为了看的清楚有些内容我删了, 更换证书我们需要保证application及orderer的MSP是相同","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/Hyperledger-Fabric组织更换证书.md","route":"/posts/afc6d6dd/","abbrlink":"afc6d6dd","title":"Hyperledger Fabric组织更换证书","date":"2021-01-24 17:34:58","updated":"2021-01-24 17:34:58","tags":["Blockchain","Hyperledger Fabric"],"categories":["Hyperledger Fabric"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","moreAnchor":"more","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<h2 id=\"前言\">前言</h2>\n<p>最近一直在研究关于如何给一个fabric的组织更换一个新的证书, 包括所有加入的通道, 所有peer和orderer.<br>\n用了很多看似完美的方法却多次测试失败, 最后总算找到一种方法.</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-json\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">{</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">    \"channel_group\"</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">: {</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">        \"groups\"</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">: {</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">            \"Application\"</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">: {</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">                \"groups\"</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4